What you need to know:

The start-up has since expanded to produce a variety of goat milk-based soaps. They also package oils and skin butters.The Cleopatra legend has it that daily baths in goat milk were the secret behind Cleopatra’s smooth, glowing skin.Goat milk is rich in selenium, a mineral that promotes a healthy skin membrane. To be incubated at KIE, one needs a solid business idea, mostly in value addition.